            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>🗓️ When to Book Day Trips</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Spring (Mar-May):</strong> Best weather, blooming almonds, comfortable temperatures</li>
                    <li><strong>Summer (Jun-Aug):</strong> Hot but coastal trips refreshing (Essaouira cooler)</li>
                    <li><strong>Fall (Sep-Nov):</strong> Perfect weather, fewer crowds, great for mountain trips</li>
                    <li><strong>Winter (Dec-Feb):</strong> Mild, waterfalls flowing, best prices, some destinations best avoided if rainy</li>
                    <li><strong>Year-Round:</strong> Most trips available daily with 300+ days sunshine!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>💰 What's Included</h3>
