                    <li><strong>Professional Guide:</strong> English/French speaking local expert</li>
                    <li><strong>Entrance Fees:</strong> Varies by trip (check individual listings)</li>
                    <li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Included on some full-day trips</li>
                    <li><strong>Flexibility:</strong> Free cancellation 24hrs before most tours</li>
                </ul>
