                    <li><strong>Comfortable Clothing:</strong> Modest dress for cultural sites, layers for temperature changes</li>
                    <li><strong>Sun Protection:</strong> Sunscreen, hat, sunglasses (Moroccan sun is strong!)</li>
                    <li><strong>Camera Ready:</strong> Charged battery and extra storage - photo opportunities everywhere</li>
